author: mcooper
msg: TRINIDAD-1232 Agent support for iPhone
Thank you Andy Schwartz for your patch.
Added the following new Agent constants:
1. org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.context.Agent.PLATFORM_IPHONE
2. org.apache.myfaces.trinidadinternal.agent.TrinidadAgent.OS_IPHONE
And also provided the AgentFactoryImpl changes required to recognize iPhone agents.

msg: * Make the ListMediator interface extend ManagedLifecycle. Indeed, all ListMediator implementations are expected to propagate lifecycle events and must therefore implement ManagedLifecycle themselves.
* SYNAPSE-451: Fixed FilterMediator to propagate lifecycle events to the else branch.
